            'We’re a Tbilisi-based team of professionals and crypto/blockchain enthusiasts who are passionate about developing user-friendly and intuitive cryptocurrency exchange with the highest liquidity in the region. We bring unique experiences to trading and we continually seek new ways to do so.\r\n\r\nAbove all, we want to make sure the on-boarding process is simple and fast. Registration and verification take only one day. We provide 40 trading pairs, and using our liquidity aggregator and matching engine, a high level of trading activity and fast order execution is guaranteed. At GEX, we have the lowest fees in the region and multiple payment options using Visa, Mastercard, Paypal, and wire transfers.\r\n\r\nStrong security is critical for our business. We are ISO 27001 compliant and adhere to the CryptoCurrency Security Standard.\r\n\r\nWe believe that continual improvement is the major key to success. We know that we can always do better. That’s why we never stop working to provide you with the exchange platform that has the best possible features and highest liquidity.',
